  <span class="verse" title="Malachi 4:2" id="Malachi-4-2">But to you who fear my name shall the sun of righteousness arise with healing in its wings. You will go out, and leap like calves of the stall.</span>
  <span class="verse" title="Malachi 4:3" id="Malachi-4-3">You shall tread down the wicked; for they will be ashes under the soles of your feet in the day that I make,&#8221; says Yahweh of Armies.</span>
  <span class="verse" title="Malachi 4:4" id="Malachi-4-4">&#8220;Remember the law of Moses my servant, which I commanded to him in Horeb for all Israel, even statutes and ordinances.</span>
